songs.lyrics:

Aye, I made an oath to my homies man
I told 'em they ain't gotta hurt no more

And it Be The Same Ones That Take Off When Everything Start Going Wrong

[Hook]
I'm employed, my rich homies ain't gotta work no more
They saying I can't put rich homies on my shirt no more
I got 'em paying for my attention ain't gon' hurt before

We Ain't Gone Hurt No more
